{"tid":713560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳支那將減進口美國原油、拋售美國國債及美元外匯儲備","createTime":"2018-06-23T02:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T04:15:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"046f4bcfc0959a57c5903c30064a4cf5a9510170","tid":713560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58353497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58353497&d=QtpeFnbj0S7RMojtUuuwcr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4cd40532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58353497&h=7c8c12db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58353497</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180623/large/1529714655_513b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180623%2Flarge%2F1529714655_513b.jpg&h=d94a465f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美支貿易戰不斷升溫，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有指</span></strong>支那反制美國加徵關稅的招數，除使出「雙敗俱傷」的拋售美國國債及美元外匯儲備外，還可以打擊美國原油出口市場。有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>透露，支那買家9月起將減少美國原油進口量，避免受貿易戰波及加徵關稅影響。<br />\n<br />\n支那是美國第二大原油採購國，規模僅次於加拿大，美國能源資訊局（EIA）數據顯示過去半年有2個月，美國出口到支那的原油量甚至超過加拿大。但支那在國際原油市場上有不少選擇，反觀美國則難找到規模像支那這麼大的替代客戶。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據悉</span></strong>，支那北京日前已將美國原油與煉製品放入報復性加稅25%的清單上，但何時生效還沒定案，這給予原油買方時間調整採購佈局，同時觀望貿易談判的結果。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，支那石化（Sinopec）目前維持7月對美採購石油量不變，但隨後則無法預計。由於航運距離的原因，支那石化廠通常提前3個月落單，即7月訂貨9月交付。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，一位與獨立煉油商進行美國原油交易的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>說，他的公司將暫停訂購在9月交付的美國原油。而支石化<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>則稱，尋找替代美國原油的其他供應絕不成為問題，如北海的福地斯原油、中東原油或者俄羅斯烏拉爾原油。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"5e4ef8533597f47e566ffde0b8fefc2cb9ca78b6","tid":713560,"uid":51701,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"第三者=小三<br />\n小龍蝦=龍蝦<br />\n為食=食沛貨<br />\n消息人士=人民日報<br />\n<br />\nappledaily = on9"},{"pid":"a7090530ecddeea7adfaffeacc12c17f23901197","tid":713560,"uid":156652,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/103830_c3d608fdca35d3289760e338ee5b178e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F103830_c3d608fdca35d3289760e338ee5b178e.jpg&h=d1a25487&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e5931f43c4acf04ced28fc2e9367784558ffd98","tid":713560,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"046f4bcfc0959a57c5903c30064a4cf5a9510170","tid":713560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58353497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58353497&d=QtpeFnbj0S7RMojtUuuwcr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4cd40532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58353497&h=7c8c12db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58353497</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180623/large/1529714655_513b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180623%2Flarge%2F1529714655_513b.jpg&h=d94a465f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美支貿易戰不斷升溫，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有指</span></strong>支那反制美國加徵關稅的招數，除使出「雙敗俱傷」的拋售美國國債及美元外匯儲備外，還可以打擊美國原油出口市場。有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>透露，支那買家9月起將減少美國原油進口量，避免受貿易戰波及加徵關稅影響。<br />\n<br />\n支那是美國第二大原油採購國，規模僅次於加拿大，美國能源資訊局（EIA）數據顯示過去半年有2個月，美國出口到支那的原油量甚至超過加拿大。但支那在國際原油市場上有不少選擇，反觀美國則難找到規模像支那這麼大的替代客戶。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據悉</span></strong>，支那北京日前已將美國原油與煉製品放入報復性加稅25%的清單上，但何時生效還沒定案，這給予原油買方時間調整採購佈局，同時觀望貿易談判的結果。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，支那石化（Sinopec）目前維持7月對美採購石油量不變，但隨後則無法預計。由於航運距離的原因，支那石化廠通常提前3個月落單，即7月訂貨9月交付。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，一位與獨立煉油商進行美國原油交易的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>說，他的公司將暫停訂購在9月交付的美國原油。而支石化<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士</span></strong>則稱，尋找替代美國原油的其他供應絕不成為問題，如北海的福地斯原油、中東原油或者俄羅斯烏拉爾原油。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁搞法隊個油價落去<br />\n其他產油國圍屌支那都似"},{"pid":"5f859adca61129749d4e7bb6bf841b23b8803da4","tid":713560,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0279d39bee269df7a5e01dff7ead6a3229cf1506","tid":713560,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d468bb64d6ecd8e942d9553813acaca1f853c2","tid":713560,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"若然屬實.jpg"},{"pid":"a360043e9ae566756f39197e80aabda10d9d3d60","tid":713560,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"攪石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501a78d55ae9a70fd96b04f93015cb3f88177472","tid":713560,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"有人要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd8154ce8b5295a07f2520f58ea2d7ba982d0e4","tid":713560,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d65ab5121567ebe419bfc815354f8def3819c65","tid":713560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"我懷疑事實係經濟衰退<br />\n<br />\n所以原油用量根本就已經係會減少<br />\n<br />\n支那將呢件事, 講成「減少入口美國原油」"},{"pid":"562ddf0ab03ccb818b5ac069f690763e3d39f7e1","tid":713560,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"屌快撚啲啦，講咗兩個幾月人哋毛都無少一條，拿拿聲亮劍啦"},{"pid":"be8c4f278407f73e4805a25c9a6fd566c1ba4b15","tid":713560,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"好多人想要美國國債，係就快，接貨"},{"pid":"9f8a927e4295a2cb33216bdec52518b9b4c36ec8","tid":713560,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"d 報導有大半都係有消息指<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係九成飛機文"}]}